Learn how to improve your study permit application to Canada in less than 10 minutes. Fix inconsistencies and common mistakes. Created by ImmInspect.com

Our Chrome extension is used to extract information from your study permit application to Canada. Once you login into your study permit application on the online portal by Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada, use our Chrome extension to pull your data from your online application into imminspect.com for review.
